Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十四話\N禰彥王子誕生 華麗的社交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.03,0:01:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.33,0:01:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心跟阿薰去看戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「紅牛」的小妙送來兩張招待券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在京都發生那麼多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.54,0:02:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾悠哉悠哉去看戲也不錯\N你說是吧 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.02,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不好\N我被害得沒時間修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還得代替劍心洗衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.09,0:02:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少發牢騷\N把洗衣也當作修行就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算什麼修行\N只是奴役罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助哥哥 跟我們一起玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好無聊 劍心哥哥在就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.27,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 你們肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.48,0:02:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣 要不要吃點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.55,0:02:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家肚子餓了\N你去烤些地瓜來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.95,0:02:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去烤地瓜？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地瓜  地瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.86,0:02:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 孩子們等不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.39,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…我衣服還沒洗完\N等一下還得打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是男人 別講話象劍心一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去烤地瓜 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.88,0:03:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 左之助居然對我頤指氣使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.52,0:03:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.12,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看戲看得太專心\N結果都忘記時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.09,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒這麼快樂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那太好了 阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 說得好像事不關己\N劍心你不覺得有趣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.77,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我比較擔心晚餐\N心情穩定不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 意思是你沒看戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你身邊\N你腦子卻在想晚餐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰 是馬車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別想瞞混過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些暴徒 覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管 殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.11,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個老人劍術很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很老了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧 老頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.23,0:04:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三個人圍攻一個老人\N太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管 把他也殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退 撤退…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.82,0:05:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 一群小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.83,0:05:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.36,0:05:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不知先生是誰\N總之感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是禰彥嗎\N你打扮成這樣幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了 振作點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題 禰彥不會這樣就受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放肆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他是誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是加卡拉達王國的鑫王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰  看來那小孩子\N並不是禰彥哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真像一個模子印出來\N怪不得小姐會弄混了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.12,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 我不知道我認錯人\N還出手打了王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我國是亞洲小國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子畢竟是\N加卡拉達王國的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了促進與日本的友好\N而來到日本的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊大夫 鑫王子身體怎樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷勢方面沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子可能不習慣長途旅行\N身體狀況不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時讓他靜養一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不嫌棄的話 就在這裏住下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.55,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前不久國王才駕崩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.46,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子被迫一肩挑起\N加卡拉達王國的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子還很年輕\N想到今後的事我就…嗚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 你不是日本人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.97,0:07:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫做村上馬凱斯\N從王子年幼時就隨侍在旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.98,0:07:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祖先是在加卡拉達\N建造日本街的日本武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.52,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的祖先是武士\N怪不得你有武士刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.32,0:07:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然剛才還受到\N緋村先生拔刀相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.26,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我村上馬凱斯老歸老\N要是再有狂徒攻擊王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就讓他嘗嘗祖先傳下來\N備前長舟劍的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時代的日本\N可找不到這種老頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 村上先生 你知道\N襲擊馬車的那些人是誰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我也想不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.76,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近外頭本來就危險\N一些武士沒飯吃就當強盜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是他們幹的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.16,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…傷腦筋\N到底該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.93,0:08:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.47,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的\N明天貴國謖重要餐會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子也以國賓身份被邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沉入谷底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 劍心你們回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.62,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧！！\N緋村先生 這小孩是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這老頭子是誰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界真是不可思議呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.54,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 這主意好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.95,0:08:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子 您的衣裳借用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干…幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.02,0:08:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.31,0:09:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一模一樣阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怪的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛要金裝人要衣裝呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相當適合你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太帥了 禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N為什麼非要我做這種打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我村上馬凱斯\N一生唯一的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.07,0:09:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能拯救我們加卡拉達王國的\N只有禰彥你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.47,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加卡拉達…這…這麼突然\N劍心 這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 被來歷不明的人破壞計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.82,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪費一個好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他拿的刀很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.33,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來以為手臂要廢掉了\N原來只是被刀背砍中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 我們一定會幹掉獵物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次就拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談一下明天的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.59,0:10:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然餐會是晚上的事\N但還是得現在就做準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.63,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先講好 當你們王子的替身\N只有今天一天哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 如果王子缺席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加卡拉達王國不只會喪失全世界的信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.54,0:11:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可能成為西方列強的餌食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.71,0:11:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是事關我國存亡的大事\N無論如何拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這些話我都會背了\N好了 到底要我怎麼做呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先請學習王子的禮節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禮節？那是什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道還要身上戴飾物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來\N好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.70,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在餐會上做出這種舉止\N是出加卡拉達王國的醜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.08,0:11:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 不論昨天或今天\N為什麼我總是這麼倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.65,0:11:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 我還請緋村他們幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心他們也有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.23,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們久等了\N禰彥 怎麼樣啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛連我們也要來陪禰彥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為只讓禰彥一人去\N心裏有點擔心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.47,0:12:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點不習慣這種打扮啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那種事 很好看哦 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們看起來像異國情侶哦\N很登對哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿薰 別貼著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.76,0:12:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 別取笑我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醜女得意起來就很難收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰是醜女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼現在要請各位學習禮節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼快就吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.18,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個味曾湯 味道怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.88,0:12:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是奶油蛋湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不發出聲音用湯匙喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個湯匙喝是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.23,0:12:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.93,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.00,0:13:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.37,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 頭一次吃這麼大塊的肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「紅牛」的牛肉火鍋\N和這個差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有筷子哦 筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有筷子  要使用那邊的刀叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 這個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.89,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不方便吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜  當然是切成小塊再吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.39,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣 這樣 這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣 這樣 這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高明高明 接下來換小綾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣這樣這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對對 小綾也很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺 小鑫在教我們\N加卡拉達的問候方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鑫的日文很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向村上學了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肩膀好僵硬 不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.96,0:14:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.63,0:14:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餐會上有人對你講話的話\N你只要回以笑容就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,免得你一開口就露出馬腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心真是 人跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是維持王子的威嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.82,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是要裝得很神氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那邊的鳥頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來為我擦鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可對鑫王子無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀對呀 你太放肆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.44,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情變成這樣\N你還是忍耐點吧 佐之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.34,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊的醜女\N別擺臭臉了 來捶背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰 這也是為了拯救加卡拉達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們忍耐下來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 快做快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾不這樣享點福\N日子真的過不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助  換另一隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醜女 再用力點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太享受了~享受啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.28,0:16:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照陸軍省得到的情報\N好像有人想奪王子的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在對進出亞洲的西歐列強而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加卡拉達成為最佳目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.00,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想殺死王子 趁國內一片混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把加卡拉達殖民地化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暗殺計劃嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.61,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日裔情報員稻城右京\N好像是那個計劃的主謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想拜託你\N請保護鑫王子的安全吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不希望這種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引起國際糾紛的事情\N在日本國內發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從行程計劃來看\N今晚是暗殺王子的唯一機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別提保不保護了\N我是不會讓那位王子死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很榮幸見到你 鑫王子殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛 你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑 你去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 別亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 我要一個人去上廁所啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 只是小便而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在道場打掃還比在這裏好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊薰 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.52,0:18:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒看到王子的身影\N他跑哪裏去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.82,0:18:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他去上廁所了\N不過…怎麼去這麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望他沒有發生萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生萬一？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.53,0:18:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可疑哦 老頭子\N你是不是有什麼事瞞著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.21,0:18:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的 有人想暗殺王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨晚的那些男人\N一定也是派來暗殺王子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.65,0:18:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明知這點  還要禰彥當替身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.29,0:18:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是為了加卡拉達王國\N我還是做了對不起你們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是下跪的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我們去找禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子 我們要取你的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.34,0:19:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 我不是鑫王子\N你看 我講的是日文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們知道\N鑫王子講日文很流利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.98,0:19:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你騙不了人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.01,0:19:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓他逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.45,0:19:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.66,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是昨天的人 又來妨礙我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鑫王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.71,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子殿下  讓我看看你的實力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 有這個就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們收拾王子 我打倒這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.11,0:20:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.85,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算付出這條命\N我也要保護禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我唯一能做的補償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加卡拉達王國的鑫王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.49,0:20:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必需在日本\N受到暴徒襲擊 死在日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.74,0:20:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.61,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全逮捕起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爺爺 你還站得起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.69,0:21:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老頭子  你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣先生 侍從長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.87,0:21:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上馬凱斯\N平安保護住鑫王子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村上先生 肩膀的傷怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.82,0:21:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托你的福 沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.86,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 謝謝你們的許多幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.30,0:21:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 不好意思 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.57,0:22:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼啦 我們長得那麼象\N也算是緣份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.61,0:22:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣這樣這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們剛才在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是王子跟我們的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.50,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個王子真的好像禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.83,0:22:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象雙胞胎一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比他更有男人氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.14,0:22:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就暫時讓你一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.34,0:22:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.69,0:25:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.59,0:25:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼大的以前從沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.93,0:25:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你在哪看到這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.80,0:25:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.40,0:25:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定把它誤以為是食物\N而帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.33,0:25:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那種事  你以為這個能吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.64,0:25:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呃…我看看 原產自中國…可以吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.94,0:25:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能吃耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.88,0:25:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 尋找消失的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.28,0:25:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名偵探狗 乃太郎  敬請期待

